org.apache.sysds.runtime.transform.encode

Class EncoderPassThrough

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.sysds.runtime.transform.encode.Encoder
      • org.apache.sysds.runtime.transform.encode.EncoderPassThrough
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class EncoderPassThrough
extends Encoder
    Simple composite encoder that applies a list of encoders in specified order. By implementing the default encoder API it can be used as a drop-in replacement for any other encoder.
    See Also:
